      <title>桌宠对话API使用文档</title>
      <link href="/article/40287.html"/>
      <url>/article/40287.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="概述"><a href="#概述" class="headerlink" title="概述"></a>概述</h1><p>本系统提供智能语音对话服务，支持完整的语音交互流程：</p><ol><li>接收用户语音输入（MP3格式）</li><li>语音识别转文本（ASR）</li><li>与讯飞大模型生成对话回复</li><li>文本转语音（TTS）生成回复音频</li><li>返回生成的语音文件路径</li></ol><h1 id="快速开始"><a href="#快速开始" class="headerlink" title="快速开始"></a>快速开始</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 调用语音对话接口</span></span><br><span class="line">curl -X POST <span class="string">&quot;http://localhost:8000/dialogue_tts/&quot;</span> \</span><br><span class="line">     -H <span class="string">&quot;X-API-Key: your_api_key&quot;</span> \</span><br><span class="line">     -F <span class="string">&quot;mp3_file=@user_audio.mp3&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="接口文档"><a href="#接口文档" class="headerlink" title="接口文档"></a>接口文档</h1><h2 id="1-语音对话处理"><a href="#1-语音对话处理" class="headerlink" title="1. 语音对话处理"></a>1. 语音对话处理</h2><ul><li><strong>URL</strong>: <code>/dialogue_tts/?reference_id=your_custom_id</code></li><li><strong>方法</strong>: POST</li><li><strong>认证</strong>: X-API-Key 请求头</li><li><strong>参数</strong>:<ul><li><code>mp3_file</code> (File): 用户上传的语音文件（MP3格式）</li><li><code>reference_id</code> (可选): 参考音频ID（用于声音克隆）</li></ul></li><li><strong>响应示例</strong>:<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;file_path&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;/static/output_1a2b3c4d.mp3&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="2-立即清理文件"><a href="#2-立即清理文件" class="headerlink" title="2. 立即清理文件"></a>2. 立即清理文件</h2><ul><li><strong>URL</strong>: <code>/clean_file/&#123;filename&#125;</code></li><li><strong>方法</strong>: DELETE</li><li><strong>认证</strong>: X-API-Key 请求头</li><li><strong>参数</strong>:<ul><li><code>filename</code>: 要删除的文件名（如<code>output_1a2b3c4d.mp3</code>）</li></ul></li></ul><h1 id="认证方式"><a href="#认证方式" class="headerlink" title="认证方式"></a>认证方式</h1><p>所有接口需在请求头中添加有效API密钥：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">headers = &#123;<span class="string">&quot;X-API-Key&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;your_api_key_here&quot;</span>&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="错误码参考"><a href="#错误码参考" class="headerlink" title="错误码参考"></a>错误码参考</h1><table><thead><tr><th>状态码</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>401</td><td>无效的API密钥</td></tr><tr><td>400</td><td>无效请求&#x2F;文件格式错误</td></tr><tr><td>500</td><td>内部处理异常</td></tr><tr><td>503</td><td>第三方服务不可用</td></tr></tbody></table><h1 id="注意事项"><a href="#注意事项" class="headerlink" title="注意事项"></a>注意事项</h1><ol><li><p><strong>文件格式要求</strong>：</p><ul><li>输入音频：MP3格式，采样率16kHz，单声道</li><li>输出音频：24kHz采样率的MP3文件</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>自动清理机制</strong>：</p><ul><li>系统会自动清理10分钟前的生成文件</li><li>重要文件请及时下载保存</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>服务依赖</strong>：</p><ul><li>需预先配置以下服务的API密钥：<ul><li>讯飞大模型（Spark Desk）</li><li>Fish-Audio 语音服务</li></ul></li></ul></li></ol><h1 id="示例代码"><a href="#示例代码" class="headerlink" title="示例代码"></a>示例代码</h1><h2 id="Python调用示例"><a href="#Python调用示例" class="headerlink" title="Python调用示例"></a>Python调用示例</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">url = <span class="string">&quot;http://localhost:8000/dialogue_tts/&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">headers = &#123;<span class="string">&quot;X-API-Key&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;your_api_key&quot;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">files = &#123;<span class="string">&quot;mp3_file&quot;</span>: <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&quot;user_input.mp3&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;rb&quot;</span>)&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">response = requests.post(url, headers=headers, files=files)</span><br><span class="line">result = response.json()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;生成的语音文件:&quot;</span>, result[<span class="string">&quot;file_path&quot;</span>])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 访问完整URL：http://localhost:8000&#123;file_path&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="音频播放示例"><a href="#音频播放示例" class="headerlink" title="音频播放示例"></a>音频播放示例</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> pydub <span class="keyword">import</span> AudioSegment</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> pydub.playback <span class="keyword">import</span> play</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">audio = AudioSegment.from_mp3(<span class="string">&quot;output.mp3&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">play(audio)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="部署说明"><a href="#部署说明" class="headerlink" title="部署说明"></a>部署说明</h1><ol><li><p>安装依赖：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install -r requirements.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>配置文件<code>config.yml</code>示例：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">app:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">api_key:</span> <span class="string">&quot;your_app_key&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">xunfei:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">app_id:</span> <span class="string">&quot;xf_app_id&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">api_key:</span> <span class="string">&quot;xf_api_key&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">patch_id:</span> <span class="string">&quot;xf_patch_id&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">fish_audio:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">api_key:</span> <span class="string">&quot;fish_api_key&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>启动服务：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python index.py</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
